 result‚Üźobject list arg;new;style;items;indents;imageindex;selimageindex
‚ćĚ Combo:list

‚ćĚ Incoming structures:
‚ćĚ   The argument may be a vector of vectors, a NL-delimited vector, or a simple character matrix.
‚ćĚ   It may also be a nested matrix (nominally 3- or 5-column), but that is only useful if 4096‚ąästyle.
‚ćĚ   Trailing blanks are stripped. Result is returned as you specified it.
‚ćĚ   In the matrix form:
‚ćĚ       [;1]‚ÜźItem text ‚čĄ [;2]‚ÜźIndent level ‚čĄ [;3]‚ÜźUnselected image ‚čĄ [;4]‚ÜźSelected image ‚čĄ [;5]‚ÜźOverlay image
‚ćĚ Dyalog output structures:
‚ćĚ   Items, Indents, ImageIndex, SelImageIndex ‚ćĚ? Overlay image not supported?

