                 arg‚Üź1‚Üď[2]5‚ÜĎ[2]0,arg ‚ćĚ Fill it out to 4 columns ‚ćĚ? The 5th column isn't supported in Dyalog
                 (items indents imageindex selimageindex)‚Üź‚äā[1]arg ‚ćĚ Assign to my property variables
             :EndIf
